***(DATE INSTALLED)
*
***(ABSTRACT)
*
*        MEMBER $MASA ON LIBRARYN.MVS CONTAINS THE MACRO '$MASA',
*         WHICH IS A MAPPING MACRO FOR THE MONSANTO ACCOUNTING SERVICE
*         AREA ( WHICH IS USED TO PRESERVE AND ACCUMULATE STEP AND JOB
*         RELATED DATA ).
*
***(MODIFICATIONS UNIQUE TO BRUSSELS)
*
*        1. ADD DOCUMENTATION ( WHICH WILL APPEAR IN RESPONSE TO THE
*           KEYWORD 'DOC=YES' ).
*        2. ADD A DSECT FOR A CONTROL BLOCK PREFIX.
*
***(LOGIC SUMMARY)
*
*        N/A
*
***(INSTALLATION)
*
*        ADD THE MEMBER TO SYS2.MACLIB ( AS MEMBER '$MASA' ).
*
***(TESTING)
*
*        N/A
